{
  "stem": "9963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What that was in that camp-- they brought in all furniture and all the belongings from all the Jewish people from the ghettos and from the little towns.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything what they had, they brought it into that camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at that camp, we sorted, you know, the clothes, pants, you know, the sizes and things like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that all was [INAUDIBLE] together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was transferred to Germany for the German population.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had over there in that camp everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whatever your heart desired, you had in that camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But on thing what we didn't have is our freedom and to eat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This what we didn't have.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I came to that camp, they ask everybody what kind of work he's doing, what kind of occupation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I told them I'm a tailor, so of course they put me into the tailor shop.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When I came into the tailor shop, I started working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I got my machine, my table to cut and design.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, I worked over there, and I had to fit the Gestapo and SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When I fit them, my hands were shaking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I felt that I cannot be responsible to be close to that people, to that kind of people, because of what they did and what they're doing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was afraid that I would lose my mind, I'd take a pair of scissors and cut some of their throat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it's not only that I would get killed, but that they would take 10, 20 people and kill.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't want to have this on my conscience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked over there another couple days, and I ask over there to the people, whatever were responsible for it, to give me a transfer.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
